Shortcuts:
ctrl + click : multiple cursors
ctrl + D or U: un/select next matching word to selected
ctrl + , : Settings View
ctrl + shift + P : Command Palette
ctrl + ↑ or ↓ : move line up or down
ctrl + shift + D : duplicate line
ctrl + / : toggle comments

My Fave Packages:
- color-picker
- pigments
- file-icons
- emmet
- highlight-selected
- autocomplete-paths
- beautify
- minimap
- minimap-highlight
